name: UNCEASING VIXEN 13:42
description: Vixens are apposed and not mimicked but complimentary of one another. They create a juxtaposition of pure paradise, an unceasing and rapturous cauldron filled with delightful rhapsodies, transported to a place where fantasy becomes an augmented reality. You are left in a state of blinding delirium, drunk with prosperity and flaring optimism. They are lying on the altar of a hallucination, which may never propagate. A monochrome version of an endless sea of perfection that would be incomprehensible in full spectrum. This bodily prism creates its saturated chroma. Undertones of a soaring sin in a delightful penance, making a bottomless cocktail not found on any mortal menu.
